snippet.title: My Next Life as a Villainess: All Routes Lead to Doom! Pirates that Stir the Waters | Switch
snippet.description:
Make my Christmas better 🎄 Please subscribe  👉 http://bit.ly/mustachegamer
It's only one click for you and it means everything to me 😍

My Next Life as a Villainess: All Routes Lead to Doom! – Pirates that Stir the Waters will launch for Switch on December 23 in Japan for 7,150 yen, developer Idea Factory announced. A limited edition will also be available for 9,350 yen. 

#MyNextLifeasaVillainess #AllRouteLeadtoDoom #PiratesthatStirtheWaters
